  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个完整的电商支付时序图，从顾客加购开始，到订单确认结束。核心流程是：顾客在前端操作，前端调用后端API，后端跟数据库和Stripe支付网关交互。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Customer",
        "Frontend",
        "Backend",
        "DB",
        "Stripe"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我先确认一下参与者的边界：Customer是外部用户，Frontend是浏览器端，Backend是服务端，DB是数据库，Stripe是第三方支付。对吗？另外，加购和结账是两个独立阶段？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Customer",
        "Frontend",
        "Backend",
        "DB",
        "Stripe",
        "Add item to cart",
        "Proceed to checkout"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。第一阶段是购物车流程：顾客点击加购，前端POST到/api/cart，后端保存到DB，然后返回成功。第二阶段是结账：顾客点击去结算，前端POST创建订单，后端生成Stripe的PaymentIntent。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "POST /api/cart",
        "Save cart item",
        "POST /api/orders",
        "Create PaymentIntent"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经画出了前半部分：Customer到Frontend的加购操作，Frontend调用Backend的cart接口，Backend和DB的往返，以及返回Cart updated。现在继续结账部分——Backend向Stripe请求clientSecret，然后传给Frontend。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Cart updated",
        "clientSecret"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "这里有个关键点：支付确认是Frontend直接和Stripe交互的，不是经过我们后端。顾客在前端输入卡号，Frontend用clientSecret调用Stripe确认支付，成功后Stripe回调Frontend。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Frontend-Stripe",
        "Confirm Payment",
        "Payment Success"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下：支付成功后，Frontend需要再通知Backend更新订单状态？还是Stripe直接通知Backend？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Notify payment success",
        "Update order as paid"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是Frontend通知Backend。Stripe回调Frontend后，Frontend再POST通知我们后端支付成功，Backend更新DB标记订单为paid，最后返回Order confirmed给前端。这样整个闭环就完成了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Notify payment success",
        "Update order as paid",
        "Order confirmed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。全链路已经画好：从加购、保存购物车，到创建订单、Stripe支付，最后通知后端更新订单状态。所有异步回调和同步调用都区分清楚了，你看还有需要调整的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Order confirmed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
  ],
